Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:04.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.52,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:13.45,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:25.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:38.62,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:41.63,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:44.41,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:52.32,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:58.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:04.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:06.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.68,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:23.15,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:36.15,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:43.21,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:50.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:56.99,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:01.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.76,0:23:09.00,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:13.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:17.69,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:25.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能打了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 稍微离开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:30.08,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}皇女 -Princess-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 到底什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以多欺少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是 重体力活就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼工夫 就结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为总能招架得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说 怎么可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是突然袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以对普通人动用魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 还没商量好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉说过吧 想为了保护他人使用我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开沉睡 把握真实 风凝吾手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…以弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是独立交易都市 三号街自卫骑士团所属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 为什么袭击我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你无关 我们要的是那把魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就别怪我们来硬的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我一句劝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦使用魔剑 无法保证你的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是在威胁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了可别怨我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那股力量是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下这招竟然还不倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那把剑是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏洛特殿下的仆从之一 多丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这把大家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地之魔剑 Claymore
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs36}Claymore：中世纪使用的双手重剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是铸刀匠的小帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用长长的槌子敲敲打打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲敲打打…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是锻造房 丽莎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用 他马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝就是锻造房 丽莎的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾名叫夏洛特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}菲洛比舍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E？ 你是帝国人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吧 帝国决定收你为臣民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾都专程来这里接你了 快收拾行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身还没习惯老百姓的玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种话可别后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我们会来硬的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来硬的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾的亲卫们应该快把这座城市的风之魔剑搞到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必客气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦 挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续打的话 就没这么便宜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打就打个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾还没说完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空和小鬼玩 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃瓦德妮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开沉睡 缠于黑暗 赐汝以终结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那咒文是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…以弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎之魔剑 埃瓦德妮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀刃剜肉 黑炎烧骨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可得小心了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前来讨教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的攻击 普通的剑不可能防住的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不巧 这是把普通的…刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾可是继承了帝国皇帝血统的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为小孩子的玩具未免太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾无论如何都需要呀 你和魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 再不去的话塞西莉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“包在我身上”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到前车之鉴吗 这个距离你赢不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.22,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玛戈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是射光之魔剑 Rhomphaia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs36}Rhomphaia：长柄逆刃刀，古色雷斯人使用的长刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开了要害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 还打算继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不带手下留情的…来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看你能坚持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 该轮到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把魔剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事的话就来抢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自我介绍了 我名叫珀涅罗珀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是Ballockknife
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs30}Ballockknife：睾丸匕首，名称来由是护手上的两颗球状物，中世纪作为男子专用匕首，骑士身份人的标配武器。 后被称为Kidney Dagger，多用在战场上杀死濒死的敌人和战友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又名 魔剑杀手的魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑杀手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛戈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要躲开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把魔剑交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦啊 早交出来早解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会…交给…你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有骨气的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在任务圆满完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切为了夏洛特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把阿丽亚…还来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强为好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖躺在那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说还来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纠缠不休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做掉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…被你…救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉给各位添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没 难为你了 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 下次别太过勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 利萨 刚才真的多亏你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体状况怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有用祈祷契约把伤口处理过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 比刚才好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长 决定怎么处置这些人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是由妾直接说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾名为夏洛特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}菲洛比舍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了皇帝血统“E”的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是帝国的…皇女殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这座城市是为了交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引渡那位“风之魔剑”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且征召BlackSmith前往帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾的要求就是以上两点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BlackSmith？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事 正如我刚才所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望再三思一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法应允这样的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也不能空手而归
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单把魔剑带回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会出个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑也是一样道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种私下交涉的行为不会被认可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以商业形式应该没有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不可以的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提倡自由交易的都市 还惧怕帝国之名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子跟谁说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对夏洛特大人这算什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人为夺走阿丽亚不惜付诸武力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么交涉 纯粹是强盗行为不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不喜欢你们对阿丽亚的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才又是购买又是交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚不是东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当做东西看待是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚和人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吃 会睡 也会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许侮辱她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不光明正大的惩治她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该马上拘捕起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市惩治皇族成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难保不会打破国家之间的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 每每纵容她们这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 你也还没有理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是更深意义上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚你也会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是克制一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 让我们打开天窗说亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在怀疑您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特{\fnsimhei}·{\r}E{\fnsimhei}·{\r}菲洛比舍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的继承了帝国皇帝的血统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请证明给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所了解的帝国 不会在非正式场合下做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真的是皇族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有“E”之名的皇族才能持有的宝剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲作为一介平民 被皇帝陛下看中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倍受宠爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但母亲被妒火中烧的妃子们千方百计赶出了宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只要让皇帝陛下刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能再次回到帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和母亲一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把宝剑是皇帝陛下赐给母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能证明妾的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就暂借一用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待问过帝国 再决定如何处理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要听那种无礼之徒的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾只为挽回母亲的名誉来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个目的 不惧怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 皇帝陛下一定会救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然夏洛特大人这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 眼下就由我们安排住所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 四把魔剑暂交我们保管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 魔剑的事没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所应当的措施
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 住所嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到这位女骑士家里借住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要住我家？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是骑士 也就是贵族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活质量应该有保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 凭什么要为袭击自己的人提供住处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费用我们出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比便宜旅馆强出百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要去家里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和某人激烈运动过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么运动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不挺好嘛 就当成友好聚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要和你们友好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么死板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下 您吃点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要点菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的小二 把菜单从头到尾给我端上来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪气十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 我可没带那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我也没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来有一阵得靠你们伺候了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顿就由妾请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好诱人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多丽丝 太没样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店的话 也不用在意礼节了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这味道相当不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别把我当成孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 夏洛特殿下还须更快快长大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 今天吃它个够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃它个够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小姐请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了吗 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多出的收下就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 里面只有三枚铜币
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不够耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 多丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 玛戈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 珀涅罗珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来迷路了十几天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预定多花了许多盘缠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮忙赊着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赊账？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 你是哪家的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉家的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 记在坎贝尔家账上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 这个也打包回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特殿下好精明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真是皇族吗！
